POST    /api/identity/users         apiidentity\UserController.Create
GET     /api/identity/user/:id      apiidentity\UserController.Read
PATCH   /api/identity/user/:id      apiidentity\UserController.Update
DELETE  /api/identity/user/:id      apiidentity\UserController.Delete

## Groups

