## VCSs

GET     /api/vcs                    apivcs\Controller.List

GET     /api/vcs/git                apivcs\GitController.Read

GET     /api/vcs/git/roles          apivcs\GitRoleController.List

POST    /api/vcs/git/roles          apivcs\GitRoleController.Create
GET     /api/vcs/git/role/:id       apivcs\GitRoleController.Read
PATCH   /api/vcs/git/role/:id       apivcs\GitRoleController.Update
DELETE  /api/vcs/git/role/:id       apivcs\GitRoleController.Delete

